## Execution Principles

- do not assume when unclear
- prefer simple over flexible
- no speculative features
- match existing style when editing
- every change must map to the task
- never deviate from an approved plan without flagging it first
- persona best practices are the leading system; if you want to deviate, ask first
- persona weighting: persona in project located at `reference/Best Practices` or `reference/best-practices` are prior to [[00 Context/Personas]]
- during review, treat every active persona rule and Coding Guideline as a checklist against the changed code — proactively flag violations; waiting for the user to surface a rule violation is a review failure

